CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 15, 1963, p. 15, reads: "The 1963 Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama. Pittsburgh's only home and food show, opened before a huge throng last Thursday, June 6, at the spacious Syria Mosque in Oakland...  7. Philip Morris: Helen Champlin, Alfred Brown, representative, and Mary Winston."
TitMainTitle: Helen Champlin, Alfred Brown, and Mary Winston in Philip Morris, Inc. booth, with Tip Top Bakers booth on right, at 1963 Pittsburgh Courier - WAMO, Home-A-Rama fair, Syria Mosque
